{
  "texts": [
    "The TTUR uses distinct learning rates of the discriminator and the generator instead of multiple update algorithms to balance the training and enable the generation of high-quality synthetic skin lesion images Goel et al. (2021) Optimized GAN CT images x x ✓ x A whale optimization algorithm (WOA) is used to balance the training of CGAN for CT image synthesis.",
    "The WOA optimizes the hyperparameters of CGAN using the hunting trick of humpback whales.",
    "It uses a strategy of finding an optimal value of the prey's location.",
    "This hunting trick is used to determine the generator's best search agents with the given discriminator which yields balanced training of GAN Biswas et al. (2019) uGAN Retinal images x x ✓ x Similar number of training steps are proposed to update the generator and discriminator models to reach the balanced state during the training of uGAN.",
    "High-quality synthetic retinal images are generated with a balanced training of uGAN"
  ]
}